items.author: Jack Rhysider
items.content:
<article>Chris Monteiro was no stranger to dark web marketplaces: drugs, weapons, crypto - you name it. But when he found a "Hitman for Hire" site selling murder, he knew it was a scam. He called them out publicly, interviewed its creator, and even hacked the site to read customers' messages.

That's when things got dark, fast.

Visit https://darknetdiaries.com/episode/156/ for a list of sources, full transcripts, and to listen to all episodes.</article>
